column2: SELECT p.ra, p.dec, z.z, z.zErr, q = CASE WHEN p.lnLExp_r < p.lnLDeV_r THEN p.DeVAB_r WHEN p.lnLExp_r > p.lnLDeV_r THEN p.expAB_r END, phi = CASE WHEN p.lnLExp_r < p.lnLDeV_r THEN p.DeVPhi_r WHEN p.lnLExp_r > p.lnLDeV_r THEN p.expPhi_r END, p.petroMag_r, p.petroMag_u, p.fracDeV_r into mydb.sample_surr_gal from PhotoObj p JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (#, #, #) n ON n.objID = p.objID JOIN Photoz z ON z.objID = n.objID WHERE p.type = # AND z.z < # + # AND z.z > # - #
